///
///   Tagged parent-pointer type. Every AST node carries one of these so
///   LSP walkers can climb from a node to its enclosing context without
///   rebuilding the tree.
///
///   Part of the Kairo Project, under the Apache License v2.0 with the
///   Kairo Runtime Library Exception.
